    "CZE": {
      "summary": "Czechia started well in a mirror-image possession battle (44.7% vs 46.5%) but were exposed by Mexico's clinical transitions in the second half. The 5-2-3 defensive shape held until the 55th minute; after conceding the opener, defensive structure collapsed and Mexico scored twice more.",
