    "MEX": {
      "summary": "Mexico delivered a composed and ruthless performance on home soil, winning 3-0 in a match where both sides were evenly matched in possession but El Tri were devastatingly clinical. Three goals from three different players — CHAVEZ, QUINONES, and FIDALGO — underlined the depth and quality of the squad.",
